    <item>
      <title>特朗普在新盟友和明确目标的带动下重返权力舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/emboldened-trump-returns-to-power-with-new-allies-clear-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普周一宣誓就职，这仅是美国历史上第二位总统失去职位后成功重返权力——这次回归巩固了他在共和党内作为持久的变革人物而非昙花一现的人物的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/emboldened-trump-returns-to-power-with-new-allies-clear-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾逮捕中国间谍嫌疑人，紧张局势加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/philippines-arrests-suspected-chinese-spy-heating-up-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾官员周一称，菲律宾当局逮捕了一名中国公民和两名菲律宾同伙，罪名是涉嫌间谍活动。此案发生在两国地缘政治紧张局势持续加剧的背景下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/philippines-arrests-suspected-chinese-spy-heating-up-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 09:59:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港首席法官承认在紧张局势下很难聘请海外人才</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/hk-chief-justice-admits-difficulty-hiring-overseas-amid-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港最高法院首席法官表示，地缘政治紧张局势阻碍了法院聘用海外法官的能力，而海外法官的存在对于外国公司来说是一个卖点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/hk-chief-justice-admits-difficulty-hiring-overseas-amid-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 09:34:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰投资局称特朗普上台后全球外商直接投资将发生改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/global-fdi-flows-will-change-under-trump-ida-ireland-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰外商投资机构负责人表示，唐纳德·特朗普今天晚些时候就任美国总统后，全球外国直接投资的格局将发生变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/global-fdi-flows-will-change-under-trump-ida-ireland-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 08:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑切斯在达沃斯论坛前夕向西班牙企业发出 Flex 警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/sanchez-surprises-investors-with-spanish-business-interventions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政六年后，西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯为欧元区最成功的主要经济体出台了出乎企业高管和投资者意料的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/sanchez-surprises-investors-with-spanish-business-interventions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国国会因尹某发生类似骚乱后保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/court-violence-tests-south-korea-s-ability-to-keep-peace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，韩国法院再次对总统尹锡烈发出拘留令几分钟后，他的一群支持者就爆发暴力冲突，开始冲击法院，其场景让人想起了 2021 年 1 月 6 日的国会山骚乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/court-violence-tests-south-korea-s-ability-to-keep-peace</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 04:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毛里求斯和英国同意查戈斯协议草案后等待特朗普批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/mauritius-says-it-has-reached-agreement-with-uk-on-chagos-draft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛里求斯表示，与英国的谈判已达成最终协议草案，将确保其对查戈斯群岛的控制，但该协议仍需得到以唐纳德·特朗普总统为首的美国新政府的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/mauritius-says-it-has-reached-agreement-with-uk-on-chagos-draft</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 03:36:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 回归引发特朗普立场审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/trump-pleases-tiktok-users-but-delay-on-app-s-ban-faces-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普承诺推迟执行禁令后，TikTok 恢复了美国服务。但尚不清楚该应用的中国母公司是否能够或愿意及时获得美国支持者，以避免永久关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/trump-pleases-tiktok-users-but-delay-on-app-s-ban-faces-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 21:59:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
